    • getCheckInCount

      public long getCheckInCount(String eventID)
      Gets the number of times an attendee has checked into an event. Throws an exception if the event ID does not exist.
      参数:
      eventID - The ID of the event.
      返回:
      The number of times an attendee has checked into an event.
      抛出:
      IllegalArgumentException - If the eventID is null.
      IllegalArgumentException - If the eventID is not found.
